dc_title_s: Comitatus Herefordiensis: Hereford shire.; Comitatvs Herefordiensis: Hereford shire;Province of Herefordshire
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Decorative title cartouche with grapes in the top right corner, and a blank cartouche with open-mouthed faces in the lower right corner. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1647 and 1658. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
